OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FThis morning will be mostly
OL,6,Fcloudy with some patchy light rain, a
OL,7,Flittle brightness possible in the
OL,8,Feast. Mainly dry and cloudy this
OL,9,Fafternoon but some brightness in the
OL,10,Feast.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FThis evening will be dry with
OL,13,Fsome late sunshine in places. Then the
OL,14,Frest of the night will be dry with
OL,15,Fvariable amounts of cloud.
OL,16,
OL,17,CWednesday:FIt will be dry with some
OL,18,Fsunshine breaking through the cloud.
OL,19,FCloudier in the west in the morning,
OL,20,Fsunniest across the east. Very warm.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
