OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,6,FMainly dry and settled on Thursday and
OL,7,FFriday with plenty of sunshine,
OL,8,Fbecoming very warm or hot. Cloudier in
OL,9,Fthe east on Saturday with some haar,
OL,10,Fbrighter and warmer west.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
